2020 excess mortality & voting patterns in CH

Assesing bias & coverage of 2015-19 models

Data

Mortality data

data = read_rds("data/BfS-closed/monthly_deaths/w_deaths_2015_2020_year_fin.Rds") %>% 
  filter(age != "<40") %>% 
  # strata with double zeroes seem to be crashing
  filter(pop_mid_poi > 0)  %>% 
  # only data till 2019
  filter(year < 2020)

data_male = data %>% 
  filter(sex == "Male") %>% 
  select(-sex) %>% 
  as.data.frame()

# data_female = data %>% 
#   filter(sex == "Female") %>% 
#   select(-sex) %>% 
#   as.data.frame()
